"\n"
"SHIELDS\n"
"\n"
"The circular Apostle shield combines clockwork motifs with flawless "
"parabolic angles to create an indestructible barrier! The brilliant aperture "
"design redistributes the force of impacts to the outer ring in a perfect "
"spiral pattern. It also produces a really tremendous clanging noise that can "
"make your teeth rattle! I suggest replacing them with brass teeth."
msgstr ""

