"\n"
"Smithing the Apostle mace requires a well-oiled mind and very steady hands. "
"Unlike the clumsy mauls and clubs warriors wield in Tamriel Above, the "
"circular flanges on this weapon orbit a perfect sphere. And I do mean "
"perfect! Even slight miscalculations in the weight or orientation of the "
"head can result in tiny dents, minor dings, and other totally unacceptable "
"imperfections."
msgstr ""

