"\n"
"LEG GREAVES\n"
"\n"
"Apostles rarely sit down. So much to do! To accommodate their busy "
"lifestyle, our brilliant predecessors invented pneumatic support girders "
"that connect to the cuisses and extend from the waist to the calf—allowing "
"the wearer to walk for as long as they wish without tiring. The quiet "
"hissing of the compressors can grate on the nerves after a while, but all "
"progress requires sacrifice!"
msgstr ""

#: 51188213-0-4752
msgctxt "51188213-0-4752"
