"\n"
"HELMETS\n"
"\n"
"First and foremost, the Clockwork Apostles must honor the Clockwork God. "
"What better way to honor him than to imitate him? Apostle helms always "
"feature a central crest that mimics the shape and motifs of Lord Seht's "
"blessed mask. Some are more ostentatious than others, but what's the point "
"of a crest if you're not going to flaunt it?"
msgstr ""

#: 51188213-0-4751
msgctxt "51188213-0-4751"
msgid "Crafting Motif 56: Apostle Helmets"
msgstr ""

