"maintaining House Hlaalu's reputation for reliability is critical to our "
"continued pre-eminence in mercantile affairs. The arms and armor of our "
"House guards and marines must adhere to strict standards in quality and "
"appearance, exemplifying that dependability expected from us by our trading "
"partners. Where possible, we adorn our items with the stylized merchant-"
"scale sigil that symbolizes the source of our power. \n"
