"MACES\n"
"\n"
"As you might expect, an assassin's wants for a mace involve puncturing heavy "
"armor more than messy bashing. Keep the striking point narrow with minimal "
"protrusions. More a hammer with a thick dagger for a head than anything else "
"I could compare it to. The two-hander is more a conventional post maul with "
"upward sloped spikes on the business ends.."
