"represent the dignity and glory of the ancient Imperial worship of the "
"Dragon God of Time. Though the Order is not technically a part of the "
"Imperial hierarchy, we nonetheless embody the virtues of the old Empire—and "
"our equipment must reflect those virtues as well. \n"
